<br>
Epicpet had Burnout IV + Muzzle, Paladin was using Natures Defender+ some 41% Haste item (I rather sure he had a Haste item from Tov quest), No other haste (No Shammy,Enchanter,Bard Eyepatch etc etc).<br>
<br>
I don't count the proces, Pally weapon proc too, but since pet was dualwielding faster than Pally 2-hander slashes I suspect pet acctually did like 2k more that the pally. But it is impossible to know so I leave that out.<br>
<br>
So basicly there you have it, a fully buffed Epic pet deal about the same dmg as an selfbuffed decent equiped L60 Paladin.<br>
