<br>
I had my 58 cleric just stand there, with unbuffed 90 CR.  The pets proc isnt effected by 66% pvp damage for some reason so it had a max of 143, however it barely ever hit this.  It was anywhere from 6 to 100 usually, around 80 at average I'd guess<br>
<br>
With malosini reducing the CR to around 20 the proc hit for 100+ very often<br>
<br>
Buffed CR up to 143 and got pretty much the same results as with 90, most mobs wont have this much<br>
<br>
So dont count on it always being 143, that barely happened even with 20CR, but the average was in the 100s <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60178"> Ylaine D'esibour- Archmage</a><br>
